sinjanju, this movie was HILARIOUS!  I normally do not like "goofy" movies, but this was sheer genius.  Well Ferrell is back.  He hasn't done a movie this funny in a long time.  Mark Wahlberg had me rolling.  Who knew he could do comedy.  The movie has a slight edge of 1970's police type drama and the intro with the Rock and Sam Jackson was hysterical.  I found myself watching that scene 3 times laughing and puzzled at the same time.  Then the conversation about the Lion versus the Tuna was CLASSIC.  I watched that 3 times because the first two times I laughed so hard, I could not breathe or really HEAR what was being said.
